Parliament, Monday, 5 March 2018 – The Standing Committee on Appropriations will tomorrow to be briefed by the Parliamentary Budget Office on the National Development Plan (NDP) and its alignment to the 2018 budget. Details of the meeting are as follows: Date: Tuesday, 06 March 2018
	Time: 10:00 am
	Venue: Committee Room M315, Third Floor, Marks Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE STANDING COMMITTEE ON APPROPRIATIONS, MS YVONNE PHOSA For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Felicia Lombard
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8285
	Cell: 081 548 7011
